pkg/runespacepb/ — vendored RuneSpace protobuf + gRPC stubs
===========================================================

runespace.pb.go, runespace_grpc.pb.go and errors.pb.go are a VERBATIM hard copy
of the generated RuneSpace data-plane stubs. They are NOT generated in this
repo — this SDK vendors them. To update: regenerate in the upstream repo and
re-copy all three .pb.go files plus both reference .proto files, then bump the
commit below.

