Notes
-----
- The embedded file-descriptor go_package
  (github.com/CryptoLabInc/runespace/pkg/runespacepb) is preserved from the
  source repo as metadata; it does not affect how this SDK imports the package,
  which is github.com/CryptoLabInc/runespace-sdk/pkg/runespacepb.
- proto/runespace/v1/*.proto are included for reference only. There is no local
  buf/protoc generation step in this repo (the stubs are vendored).
- errors.pb.go defines ErrorReason, the machine-readable cause the server
  attaches to failed RPCs via a google.rpc.ErrorInfo status detail (Domain
  "runespace.v1"); the gRPC status code stays the coarse classifier.
